<subSubSection id="DF204B502427880E0821BC64475174C0" pageId="39" pageNumber="84" type="type material">
<paragraph id="2B1F6B94524041C7E61688323279D4B5" pageId="39" pageNumber="84">Type material.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="9750F5713DAE85D4A3296C06E976A7B8" pageId="39" pageNumber="84">Holotype CUMZ 6254 (Fig. 10C). Measurement: shell height 4.6 mm, shell width 7.3 mm, and with 6 whorls. Paratypes: CUMZ 6032 (2 shells), 6236 (6 specimens in ethanol), and NHMUK 20130682 (2 shells) from the type locality.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
